282
00:28:17,445 --> 00:28:18,571
I was just waiting for you.

283
00:28:22,575 --> 00:28:23,952
My whole life,

284
00:28:25,912 --> 00:28:27,414
I waited for you

285
00:28:29,499 --> 00:28:30,917
to come and find me.

286
00:28:34,045 --> 00:28:35,505
