you must leave at once!

328
00:32:58,434 --> 00:33:01,479
How dare you spew such nonsense
on this happy day?

329
00:33:01,562 --> 00:33:02,647
Your Majesty.

330
00:33:03,481 --> 00:33:04,857
I sincerely beg you.

331
00:33:04,983 --> 00:33:07,193
