with the remnants of Seoraewon

362
00:34:57,136 --> 00:34:59,055
to disseminate The Story of Ho Dam,

363
00:34:59,764 --> 00:35:01,682
exhibiting her disrespect
toward Your Majesty.

364
00:35:02,100 --> 00:35:04,310
